  "response": "As of my knowledge cutoff in October 2023, there is no publicly available information detailing the exact amount Mercedes-Benz spent on product placement in the \"Jurassic World\" films. Product placement deals between brands and movie studios are often confidential, and specific financial terms are typically not disclosed to the public.\n\nHowever, Mercedes-Benz has a history of engaging in product placement across various films and media to increase brand visibility and associate their vehicles with high-profile entertainment projects. If you're interested in detailed information about their marketing strategies or specific partnerships, it might be helpful to consult industry reports, press releases from Mercedes-Benz, or interviews with marketing executives from the company.\n\nIf any new information has been released after October 2023, I would recommend checking the latest news sources or the official Mercedes-Benz corporate communications for updates.",
